'''阿灵顿排屋'''（Arlington Row）位于英格兰[[格洛斯特郡|格洛斯特郡]][[拜伯里|拜伯里]]民政教区的阿灵顿村，建于14世纪晚期，是一家羊毛店，在17世纪后期改建为织工小屋 。这是一座一级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]],<ref name="nhle"/> 由[[英國國民信託|英國國民信託]]拥有。<ref name="nationaltrust">{{cite web | title = Bibury | url = http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/bibury/ | publisher = National Trust | date =  | accessdate = 2013-08-07 | archive-date = 2013-08-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130803234657/http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/bibury/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

阿灵顿排屋在奥克沃德山上，是一个全国著名的建筑[[保护区|保护区]]，出现在所有英国护照上。<ref name="lovingthecotswolds">{{cite web |title=Arlington Row, Bibury |url=http://www.lovingthecotswolds.com/arlington-row-bibury |publisher=Loving the Cotswolds |accessdate=2019-05-12 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914035830/http://www.lovingthecotswolds.com/arlington-row-bibury |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这是一个受欢迎的旅游景点，<ref name=bbc>{{cite web | title = Gloucestershire – History – Day Out: The South East Cotswolds | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/gloucestershire/content/articles/2008/10/23/dayout_se_cotswolds_video_feature.shtml | publisher = BBC | date = Jan 2009 | accessdate = 2013-08-07 | archive-date = 2012-11-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121113090337/http://www.bbc.co.uk/gloucestershire/content/articles/2008/10/23/dayout_se_cotswolds_video_feature.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref> 可能是[[科茨沃尔德|科茨沃尔德]]最上镜的景点之一<ref>{{cite web |title=Arlington Row, Bibury |url=http://www.bibury.com/arlington-row/ |publisher=Bilbury |accessdate=2019-05-12 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015236/https://www.bibury.com/arlington-row/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==历史==
小屋建于1380年，是修道院的羊毛店。<ref>{{NHLE|desc=Arlington Row|num=1155677|accessdate=28 August 2016}}</ref>在17世纪后期改造成一排织工的小屋，有一些则是17世纪末或18世纪初新建<ref name="nhle"/>。这里生产的布挂在架子上干燥，然后被送到阿灵顿磨坊漂洗。<ref>{{cite web |title=Bibury Village, Gloucestershire |url=https://www.biburyvillage.uk/arlingtonrow.html |website=www.biburyvillage.uk |accessdate=2019-07-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190718161212/http://www.biburyvillage.uk/arlingtonrow.html |archivedate=2019-07-18}}</ref>  

它于1929年由[[皇家艺术学院|皇家艺术学院]]保护，1970年代由[[英國國民信託|英國國民信託]]修复<ref name="nhle"/>。

这里也是电影和电视的拍摄地点，最著名的是电影《[[星塵傳奇|星塵傳奇]]》<ref>{{cite web |title=Filming Location Matching "Arlington Row, Bibury, Cirencester, Gloucestershire, England, UK" |url=https://www.imdb.com/search/title?locations=Arlington%20Row,%20Bibury,%20Cirencester,%20Gloucestershire,%20England,%20UK&ref_=ttloc_loc_2 |publisher=IMDB |accessdate=2019-05-12}}</ref>和《[[BJ單身日記_(電影)|BJ單身日記]]》。<ref name="gloucestershireecho.co.uk">{{cite web |url=http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Passport-picture-influx-tourists-according-Bibury/story-21747410-detail/story.html |title=Passport picture not behind influx of tourists according to Bibury residents |accessdate=2014-08-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808042758/http://www.gloucestershireecho.co.uk/Passport-picture-influx-tourists-according-Bibury/story-21747410-detail/story.html |archivedate=2014-08-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://biburyshop.blogspot.co.uk/2010/05/japanese-and-english.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2014-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218193816/http://biburyshop.blogspot.co.uk/2010/05/japanese-and-english.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gloucestercitizen.co.uk/Beauty-spots-appear-new-passports/story-11931593-detail/story.html |title=Beauty spots to appear in our new passports |accessdate=2014-08-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924022813/http://www.gloucestercitizen.co.uk/Beauty-spots-appear-new-passports/story-11931593-detail/story.html |archivedate=2015-09-24}}</ref>

